\v 27 \x - \xo 5:27 \xt TP 20.14; GT 5.18\x*Yesu da saŇčbeŇček yaŇč yag…®t, ‚ÄúAe gen k…®nda bab…®k da ab…®dawit uŇčun ji k…®l…® nandawit. Gen uŇčun yaŇč:  
