\v 33 \x - \xo 5:33 \xt MS 19.12; IDT 30.2; GT 23.21\x*Yesu da saŇčbeŇček yaŇč yag…®t, ‚ÄúAe gen k…®nda bab…®k da ab…®dawit uŇčun ji k…®l…® nandawit. Gen uŇčun yaŇč:  
