\v 38 \x - \xo 5:38 \xt TP 21.24; MS 24.20; GT 19.21\x*Yesu da saŇčbeŇček yaŇč yag…®t, ‚ÄúAe gen k…®nda bab…®k da ab…®dawit uŇčun ji k…®l…® nandawit. Gen uŇčun yaŇč:  
