\v 43 \x - \xo 5:43 \xt MS 19.18\x*Yesu da saŇčbeŇček yaŇč yag…®t, ‚ÄúAe gen k…®nda bab…®k da ab…®dawit uŇčun ji k…®l…® nandawit. Gen uŇčun yaŇč:  
